description: Russia-Ukraine War LIVE Updates: As the Russian attack on Ukrainian cities continues, President Zelenskyy said on Saturday that “meaningful negotiations” are the “only chance for Russia to reduce the damage from its own mistakes”. After days of progress, talks between the two nations have hit a roadblock with Russia accusing Ukraine of dragging on peace talks. According to UN estimates, nearly 6.5 million people have been internally displaced in Ukraine since the war began. Stay with IndiaToday.in for LIVE updates.
